<br />
I had talked to my neighbor about being part of it and he would welcome me in but I don&#39;t know if it&#39;s really worth it.<br />
<br />
These things do make money for the most part, the part of town they are in is really nice and I think they could go over well.  I&#39;d much rather see how their first two stores go before getting into anything though.  The brother and brothers friend are only going to be there a few hours a week and hope to find good managers to run it, which is somewhat tough with how little they pay these guys.<br />
<br />
